    "The spate of real-world attacks on manufacturing and CI operational technology (OT), and their consequences reiterate the value in timely detection of these attacks and subsequent actions to bring these systems into a safe and non-compromised state.In this work, we use the Secure Water Treatment (SWaT) [9] testbed as a use case in ICS anomaly detection."
